constraints_details.result: Hinterland Lower Lea Valley including Stratford

description: Demolition of the existing buildings, with the exception of 21-22 Gillender Street (Magnolia House), and redevelopment of the site to provide 307 residential units (Use Class C3), 1,815 sq m of commercial floorspace (Use Class B1) and 100 sq m of flexible commercial/retail floorspace (Use Class A1/A3/B1) within three buildings of 8 storeys (42.9m AOD), 17 storeys (67.0m AOD) and 20 storeys (78.5m AOD) with public and private amenity spaces, together with disabled car parking, cycle parking and associated landscaping.
